{"tid":1304330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"200人包圍油塘「連儂牆」 叫囂指罵青年","createTime":"2019-07-10T14:47:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T15:53:12.000Z","uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cc10a704687f072849d5c93893a75a91964dd6d5","tid":1304330,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:47:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190710/large/1562766743_39cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190710%2Flarge%2F1562766743_39cd.jpg&h=d3fd00f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190710/large/1562766741_f060.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190710%2Flarge%2F1562766741_f060.jpg&h=aff41612&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人出手推撞青年。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190710/large/1562766741_0ba4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190710%2Flarge%2F1562766741_0ba4.jpg&h=10677545&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n油塘站外亦有人指罵青年。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190710/large/1562766979_9c8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190710%2Flarge%2F1562766979_9c8b.jpg&h=0241c351&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190710/large/1562767094_8213.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190710%2Flarge%2F1562767094_8213.jpg&h=f49b07e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4412489697cbc5036a8e6deafb6bb52191f3f56","tid":1304330,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:47:50.000Z","msg":"反送中惡法運動席捲全城，各區市民自發建立「連儂牆」，將心聲寫上便利貼，為港人打氣。不過，今日及昨日各區均出現「暴力市民」疑不滿「連儂牆」，動手撕去便利貼。<br />\n<br />\n晚上8時許，油塘大本型外數名青年整理「連儂牆」，其間大批中年男子走近指罵挑釁，雙方發生衝突，氣氛緊張，其間有人怒罵「咁多度唔搞搞油塘？」由於對方恃人多勢眾，約2百人包圍數名青年喝罵，情況一片混亂，發生肢體碰撞。<br />\n<br />\n大批警員接報持盾牌到場維持秩序，數十名青年亦趕至聲援，雙方繼續互相指罵，不時有青年遭人包圍，警員將其隔開，並協助青年到安全位置。"},{"pid":"235ec1bb5dc5eb959163c2290492ddbc5817a502","tid":1304330,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:48:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190710/59809878\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190710%2F59809878&d=RGEj3L6UPYZQbhamDwVV3ckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=9b4c8ccc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190710%2F59809878&h=368b7310\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190710/59809878</a>"},{"pid":"469453fa9b7abda1bc4f420bb38175461765d117","tid":1304330,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:49:13.000Z","msg":"咪由得佢地叫囂囉 咁多人唔通郁手咩<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Be Water</span></span>"},{"pid":"6a8e13974c5f1e9549a32d6717a45cc5c0c84d8d","tid":1304330,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"469453fa9b7abda1bc4f420bb38175461765d117","tid":1304330,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:49:13.000Z","msg":"咪由得佢地叫囂囉 咁多人唔通郁手咩<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Be Water</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:50:06.000Z","msg":"拆完可以再起<br />\n最緊要保護到自己身份同人身安全"},{"pid":"19e7b9009296dabc66dea094c926fadd241ecf3e","tid":1304330,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:50:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd42179f79c9422f7f1f2ee646131056b2f5ed2","tid":1304330,"uid":2